===Letter===
'''מ''' (spelled ''[[mem]]'') is the thirteenth letter of the [[Hebrew]] alphabet.<br>
'''ם''' is the final form of the letter ([[sofeet]]), used only at the end of a word.

מ also represents the [[numeral]] 40 in Hebrew numbering.

* '''Last''': [[ל]]
* '''Next''': [[נ]]

